snippet.title: Toe II Toe - a 20 second slugfest
snippet.description:
Toe II Toe is a fast-paced mini fighting game in a retro gameboy style for the 20 second Game Jam on itch.io! You have your feet planted on the ground, ready for a slugfest. Punch, duck, or block your way to victory!

https://plazatin.itch.io/toe-20-toe

BOOKMARKS:
Single Player
[00:10] 1P vs CPU - Win by Knock Out
[00:35] 1P vs CPU - Win by Time Over
[01:01] 1P vs CPU - Lose by Knock Out

Multiplayer
[01:29] 1P vs 2P - 2P Win by Knock Out
[01:54] 1P vs 2P - Draw by Double Knock Out
[02:18] 1P vs 2P - 2P Win by Knock Out

[02:41] Leaderboards
